  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#13273C" class="c1">Trust me, Retlom is a Necromancer.  The first evidence supporting this claim is that  Gnomes can't be Shadow Knights.<br>
<br>
I'm not entirely sure what his clothing is, since it's not robes.  I suppose it could be one of those Gnomish Environmental Suits or something (which doesn't drop).  But since I've never confirmed seeing a Gnome wearing one, I can only speculate.<br>
<br>
I've noticed that the Grobs (Bindlegrob, Findlegrob, and Sindlegrob) in Rathe mountains are similarly attired and they are also Gnomish Necromancers.<br>
<br>
Believe me, if Meldrath were an SK, he'd have a sword or something and his pet would be really weak.  When I came across him at about level 37, both Meldrath and his pet were blue to me.  He'd also use his harmtouch if he were an SK.  Lastly, if Meldrath were an SK, he'd melee more and cast less.  Meldrath casts a lot.  He's a Necromancer.<br>
<br>
